{"tid":1280194,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"IB有新野 銀行存款轉存計劃","createTime":"2019-07-03T01:40:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T02:48:31.000Z","uid":32511,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"066b8576f88ba22620ae70d94156f63a53da565c","tid":1280194,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:40:40.000Z","msg":"Interactive Brokers很高興地宣布一項全新的計劃，為您經紀賬戶中的現金提供多一重的安全保障。 &quot;受保銀行存款轉存計劃&quot;由聯邦存款保險公司（FDIC）為您的賬戶現金餘額提供最高達250萬美元的保障。加上現有的證券投資者保護公司（SIPC）為您賬戶提供的250,000美元保障，您的被保險資金金額將達275萬美元。超過275萬美元的現金餘額將根據美國證監會客戶保護規則15c3-3的要求，由本公司的股本（超過60億美元）保障。點擊連結了解有關本計劃的更多信息。<br />\n<br />\n參加本計劃不會影響您的賬戶功能或交易權限。您的賬戶餘額將繼續享有有競爭力的利息，且賬戶中的資金仍可在全球100多個交易所用於股票、期權、期貨、外匯及債券交易。"},{"pid":"8c43f5ba4d3c6a7fbd83132ef5f6aa52358052bd","tid":1280194,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:47:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.interactivebrokers.com/cn/index.php?f=28303\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.interactivebrokers.com%2Fcn%2Findex.php%3Ff%3D28303&d=ItsvLBlInL5d1alZeSWtsM4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=6e08632e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.interactivebrokers.com/cn/index.php?f=28303</a>"},{"pid":"adc5729f15024450ce66b04cb03a0766e9901bb1","tid":1280194,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:52:32.000Z","msg":"啫係IB做埋銀行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7150eaed5a8155376c0f3b62b596279a364d37f6","tid":1280194,"uid":197540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:53:45.000Z","msg":"唔係好明, 即係點?"},{"pid":"6d29de8de54b6fb65361f2373848ab8d99291c4e","tid":1280194,"uid":22337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:55:13.000Z","msg":"又係唔包香港？"},{"pid":"33aef0907aefe188aa457272f8643eb63abcc870","tid":1280194,"uid":215905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:58:20.000Z","msg":"受保銀行存款轉存計劃<br />\n通過加入受保銀行存款轉存計劃，<span style=\"